  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the toasted pumpkin seeds and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the crushed puffed rice cereal and cook for 2 minutes, until lightly browned.",
    "Add the chickpeas, Thai chili sauce, lime juice, fish sauce, and brown sugar. Stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes, until the chickpeas are coated in the sauce.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with additional toasted pumpkin seeds if desired."
